news.title: Cu Chi Tunnels Luxury Tour - Morning or Afternoon
news.content: Hear stories of the American-Vietnam war as you discover the maze-like Cu Chi Tunnels, a 136-mile (220 kilometers) network of underground tunnels used by the Viet Cong soldiers.
news.author: Long Huy

news.title: Ha Long Bay Cruise Day Tour - best selling: Kayaking, Swimming, hiking & Lunch
news.content: Come ready to party on this fun-filled Halong Bay boat tour. Departing Hanoi's old quarter early, you’ll get a full day out on the water amongst the thousands of islands that dot the sea in this unique landscape. Enjoy kayaking through tunnels and swimming at the beach
news.author: Kuro

news.title: Ba Na Hills with Golden Bridge Private Tour
news.content: Get away from the crowds and see the best of Ba Na Hills on this private tour. After pickup from your hotel, you’ll ride the famous cable car, wander across the famous Golden Bridge, explore Linh Ung Pagoda, Loc Uyen Garden, and Quan Am Pavilion, and feast on an authentic Vietnamese buffet. With your English-speaking guide leading the way
news.author: PD
